                </svg>
                Changes in Family Situation
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Marriage, the birth of a child, children growing older and requiring different types of care, or even a divorce can significantly alter your family's healthcare requirements. For instance, welcoming a new baby means you'll need good maternity and pediatric coverage. As children grow, their needs change, and your family plan should adapt accordingly.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
