                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Changes in Financial Situation
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">A new job, a salary increase, or a period of financial tightening can all influence what you can afford or what you prioritize in a health insurance plan. You might be able to afford more comprehensive supplementary coverage, or you might need to find ways to reduce your monthly premium expenses by finding cheaper health insurance.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
