                </svg>
                Relocation within Switzerland
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Health insurance premiums vary considerably from one canton to another. If you move from a canton with lower average premiums to one with higher costs (e.g., Zurich or Geneva), your current insurance plan might become disproportionately expensive or no longer offer the best network in your new location. Changing to an insurer or model that is more competitive in your new canton of residence is often a smart move.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
